data.description: Beautiful mid century craftsman style home with a creek on 1.9 acres in the heart of Kalispell. Featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms this home is sure to impress. A wood stove to keep you warm during those chilly winter days and elbow room to spare, this is truly an oasis. Home has been recently updated to include, new wiring, windows flooring,siding, and roofing. New fencing around the entire property and crossfenced to seperate the main yard from the field. A large multi bay shop is perfect for those projects or storing toys. Multiple outbuildings incude a heated office/shed and several storage sheds.
